Summary: flying in from australia to los angeles i saw this object on the star board side window of the plane
divs: Sighting Detailsflying in from Australia to Los Angeles. I caught a view of this object from the left hand side of the plane.Thank god i had camera in hand,i turned trying to centre the object in my lens unfortunately the object was moving way to fast and this all the camera caught. I know it was not a bird.not at that elevation. Photo was taken with a Kodak Digital C310.
